\c 1
\s Iminikelo yokutshiswa
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimbiza uMozisi yakhuluma kuye\x + Eks. 19.3.\x* isethenteni lenhlangano yathi\x + Eks. 40.34,35. Nani 12.4,5.\x*:
\v 2 Khuluma kubantwana bakoIsrayeli uthi kubo: Nxa umuntu wakini esondeza umnikelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 22.18,19.\x*, lizasondeza umnikelo wenu ovela ezifuyweni, ovela enkomeni, loba ovela ezimvini.
\p
\v 3 Uba umnikelo wakhe ungumnikelo wokutshiswa ovela enkomeni, uzanikela iduna elingelasici\x + 1.10. Eks. 12.5.\x*, alinikele emnyango wethente lenhlangano, ngokuthanda kwakhe, phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 4 Uzabeka isandla sakhe enhlokweni yomnikelo wokutshiswa\x + Eks. 29.10,15,19. Levi 3.2,8,13; 4.4,15,24,29,33; 8.14,18,22; 16.21.\x*, njalo wemukelelwe yena\x + 22.27.22.21. Isa. 56.7. Roma 12.1. Fil. 4.18.\x*, ukumenzela inhlawulo yokuthula\x + 4.20,26,31,35. Nani 15.25. 2 Lan. 29.23,24. Levi 9.7. 16.24.\x*.
\v 5 Uzalihlaba ijongosi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*; lamadodana kaAroni, abapristi, azanikela igazi, afafaze igazi elathini inhlangothi zonke\x + 3.8. 2 Lan. 35.11. Heb. 12.24. 1 Pet. 1.2.\x*, elisemnyango wethente lenhlangano.
\v 6 Uzahlinza umnikelo wokutshiswa\x + 3.8. 2 Lan. 35.11. Heb. 12.24. 1 Pet. 1.2.\x*, awusike ngeziqa zawo\x + 1.6,12; 8.20.\x*.
\v 7 Njalo amadodana kaAroni umpristi azafaka umlilo elathini, ahlele inkuni phezu komlilo\x + Gen. 22.9.\x*.
\v 8 Amadodana kaAroni, abapristi, azahlela-ke izitho\x + 1.6,12; 8.20.\x*, inhloko lamahwahwa\x + 1.12; 8.20.\x*, phezu kwenkuni ezisemlilweni ophezu kwelathi.
\v 9 Kodwa imibilini yalo lemilenze yalo uzakugezisa ngamanzi\x + 1.13. Eks. 12.9.\x*; njalo umpristi uzakutshisa konke elathini, \add kube\add* ngumnikelo wokutshiswa, umnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo\x + Eks. 29.18,25,41. Levi 1.13,17; 2.2,3,9,10,11,16; 3.3,5,9,11,14,16; 4.35.\x* oloqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 1.13,17; Gen. 8.21.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Njalo uba umnikelo wakhe uvela emhlanjini, owezimvu loba owembuzi, kube ngumnikelo wokutshiswa, uzasondeza iduna elingelasici;
\v 11 uzalihlabela eceleni kwelathi ngenyakatho\x + 1.5.\x*, phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*; njalo amadodana kaAroni, abapristi, azafafaza igazi lalo elathini inhlangothi zonke.
\v 12 Uzalisika ngeziqa zalo, lenhloko yalo lamahwahwa alo\x + 1.6,12; 8.20.\x*; lompristi uzakuhlela phezu kwenkuni ezisemlilweni ophezu kwelathi.
\v 13 Kodwa uzagezisa imibilini lemilenze ngamanzi; lompristi uzakunikela konke, akutshise elathini; kungumnikelo wokutshiswa, umnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo oloqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\p
\v 14 Uba-ke umnikelo wakhe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ungumnikelo wokutshiswa owezinyoni, uzanikela umnikelo wakhe uvela emajubeni\x + 5.7; 12.8; Luka 2.24.\x* loba amaphuphu enkwilimba.
\v 15 Umpristi alisondeze elathini, atshuphune inhloko yalo, alitshise elathini, legazi lalo likhanyelwe eceleni kwelathi,
\v 16 asuse isidlelo salo lensiba zalo, akulahle eceleni kwelathi ngempumalanga\x + 6.10; 10.12.\x*, endaweni yomlotha,
\v 17 aliqhaqhe ngempiko zalo, angalehlukanisi\x + Gen. 15.10.\x*; umpristi alitshise-ke elathini, phezu kwenkuni ezisemlilweni; kungumnikelo wokutshiswa\x + 1.9,13.\x*, umnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo oloqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
